    <h2 class="section-title">Monogram model families in heavy SoCal service rotation.</h2>

    <p class="lead">A representative sample of Monogram model families our techs service routinely. Not exhaustive — Monogram's US catalog covers more variants — but covers the units that show up most often on our route.</p>

