<!-- 05 PRICING -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-number">05, Pricing</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What GE Monogram repair costs in Southern California.</h2>

    <p class="lead">Diagnostic is $89, applied toward the repair when you approve the work. Monogram pricing sits in the mid-luxury repair tier — parts ship from GE Appliances' Louisville KY distribution backbone (typical 2-5 day lead on less-common items; common wear parts for the dominant ZISS / ZIC / ZDT / ZDP series on the truck for same-day completion). The US-supply advantage on parts lead time vs European luxury brands is real and reflects in faster turn on the typical Monogram repair.</p>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-label">Diagnostic</div>
        <div class="price-amount">$89</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Waived when you approve repair</div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-label">Standard band</div>
        <div class="price-amount">$185–$425</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Ice maker fill valve · water valve · door gasket · igniter · halogen lamp · sensor</div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-label">Major component</div>
        <div class="price-amount">$345–$680</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Ice maker assembly · evap / condenser fan · control board · magnetron · door hinge · oven element</div>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-label">Compressor / sealed-system</div>
        <div class="price-amount">$580–$880</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Out-of-warranty compressor swap · refrigerant work · evaluated on 10+ year unit</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="price-note">Repair-vs-replace math on Monogram consistently favors repair through year 12-15. Replacement-unit pricing: ZISS420 built-in side-by-side runs $8,000-$12,000, ZISS480 48-inch $10,000-$14,000, ZIC column installation $10,000-$15,000+, ZDP professional range $5,000-$9,000, Advantium speed oven $2,500-$3,500, ZDT dishwasher $2,500-$3,500. Against those numbers, an $880 compressor swap on a year-12 ZISS or a $680 control board on a ZDP range is a comparatively small expenditure to recover another 8-10 years of service life. We document the math at diagnostic before authorization, every time.</p>
